<HEADLINE> Sinopec Earns 178 Billion Yuan in First Half </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, July 19 (Xinhua) -- The China National Petrochemical
Corp. (Sinopec) enjoyed good economic returns in the first six
months this year, with sales income topping 178 billion yuan, up
27.3 percent over the same period of last year.
</P>
