Projects to be benefited total 114 ranging from publicity to
database development and market studies planned to help
communities attract foreign investors.
</P>
<P>
Every 1 billion Canadian dollar (about 680 million U.S. dollar)
foreign investment creates 10,000 to 12,000 jobs in Canada,
according to the official statistics. 
