natural disasters, epidemics and other emergencies nationwide, is
under way.
</P>
<P>
Once completed, the network will include central and local
medicine storage facilities storing some 1.2 billion yuan (145
million U.S. dollars) worth of medicines and medical appliances,
Chen Xianxia, director of the Comprehensive Affairs Division of
the Pharmaceutical Department, State Economic and Trade Commission,
said in an interview with China Daily. 
